{"trip_id":"2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque","epigraph":{"quote":"I had the best night's sleep ever. Best view ever."},"moments":[{"seq":2,"place_id":"oxford-uk","lon":-1.2578499,"lat":51.7520131,"place":"Oxford, UK","date":"2017-04-22","role":"transit_stop","quote":"Jenny gave us lovely pasta.","images":[]},{"seq":3,"place_id":"stalisfield-green-kent-uk","lon":0.79933,"lat":51.2413981,"place":"Stalisfield Green, Kent, UK","date":"2017-04-22","role":"overnight_base","quote":"The supper at 8 (booked head) was delicious. Rump of Kent lamb + cod Stalisfield Green.","images":[]},{"seq":4,"place_id":"folkestone-eurotunnel","lon":1.1156,"lat":51.093,"place":"Folkestone (Eurotunnel)","date":"2017-04-22","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"We left [?Tinder] a went south to near the Channel Tunnel.","images":[]},{"seq":5,"place_id":"reims-france","lon":4.031926,"lat":49.2577886,"place":"Reims, France","date":"2017-04-22","role":"main_stop","quote":"There's a Fair in the square. But I don't want to go on the rides. I must be getting old.","images":[]},{"seq":6,"place_id":"revigny-sur-ornain-france","lon":4.9870514,"lat":48.8284503,"place":"Revigny-sur-Ornain, France","date":"2017-04-22","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Everything shut up, a free night. But oh so cold.","images":[{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0277_R_1.webp","w":831,"h":900,"caption":"Reims. 1974. Chagall. Made in Reims left lancet. Virgin & Child.","type":"postcard"},{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0278_L_1.webp","w":833,"h":900,"caption":"Kéms XIII Northern doorway. Angel of the smile","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":7,"place_id":"lucerne-switzerland","lon":8.3058123,"lat":47.052144,"place":"Lucerne, Switzerland","date":"2017-04-22","role":"transit_stop","quote":"Past Lucerne. Didn't see Bridge.","images":[]},{"seq":8,"place_id":"eich-lucerne-switzerland","lon":8.1691162,"lat":47.1515249,"place":"Eich, Lucerne, Switzerland","date":"2017-04-22","role":"overnight_base","quote":"A room facing village was 220, but we faced lake (240€) which had a glorious view all evening + all night.","images":[]},{"seq":9,"place_id":"pavia-italy","lon":9.1378251,"lat":45.0368546,"place":"Pavia, Italy","date":"2017-04-22","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We had coffee, bought cake & cycled back to the van.","images":[]},{"seq":10,"place_id":"sestri-levante-italy","lon":9.3958627,"lat":44.2714526,"place":"Sestri Levante, Italy","date":"2017-04-22","role":"overnight_base","quote":"In the evening we had supper next to an Italian couple who now run a 22 bed guest house.","images":[{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0280_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":755,"caption":"Corniglia","type":"photo"}]},{"seq":11,"place_id":"montalcino-italy","lon":11.4902818,"lat":43.0575578,"place":"Montalcino, Italy","date":"2017-04-22","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Such wonderful views in a full 180°, & just over the ridge there are views the other way. Mile after mile. 100 miles. Sunshine.","images":[{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0281_L_1.webp","w":893,"h":900,"caption":"Abbey of Sant'Antimo, Montalcino, Tuscany","type":"photo"}]},{"seq":12,"place_id":"pienza-italy","lon":11.6789076,"lat":43.0765485,"place":"Pienza, Italy","date":"2017-04-22","role":"main_stop","quote":"As we left we saw Anna & boyfriend loading her dog onto the back of the motor bike.","images":[{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0282_L_1.webp","w":513,"h":403,"caption":"dog box on motorbike","type":"sketch"}]},{"seq":13,"place_id":"assisi-italy","lon":12.6146669,"lat":43.0711952,"place":"Assisi, Italy","date":"2017-04-22","role":"overnight_base","quote":"It was a shock to see soldiers with machine guns at the Basilica","images":[{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0284_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":851,"caption":"Assisi Basilica. Crucifixion. Giotto 1267-1337","type":"postcard"},{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0283_R_1.webp","w":888,"h":869,"caption":"Assisi - Basilica di S. Francesco","type":"ticket"}]},{"seq":14,"place_id":"perugia-italy","lon":12.4029962,"lat":43.1070321,"place":"Perugia, Italy","date":"2017-04-22","role":"main_stop","quote":"The Piero della Francesca altarpiece was magnificent. I could have sat looking at it for ours.","images":[{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0284_R_1.webp","w":667,"h":644,"caption":"Piero d.l. Francesca","type":"photo"}]},{"seq":15,"place_id":"san-feliciano-lake-trasimeno-italy","lon":12.1679561,"lat":43.1176557,"place":"San Feliciano, Lake Trasimeno, Italy","date":"2017-04-22","role":"overnight_base","quote":"An odd bird here - horizontal black + white stripes + a red hat","images":[{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0285_R_1.webp","w":900,"h":691,"caption":"Tramonto sull'Isola Polvese - Lake Trasimeno","type":"postcard"},{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0286_R_1.webp","w":441,"h":900,"caption":"Museo Diocesano Cortona admission ticket with Beato Angelico Annunciazione","type":"ticket"}]},{"seq":16,"place_id":"cortona-italy","lon":11.9850623,"lat":43.2752976,"place":"Cortona, Italy","date":"2017-04-22","role":"main_stop","quote":"we saw the gorgeous Fra Angelico Annunciation.","images":[]},{"seq":17,"place_id":"siena-italy","lon":11.467561,"lat":43.1672059,"place":"Siena, Italy","date":"2017-04-22","role":"overnight_base","quote":"The colours in Christ's passion are fabulous + fresh","images":[{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0287_L_1.webp","w":811,"h":451,"caption":"Siena crypt frescoes interior","type":"photo"},{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0287_R_1.webp","w":804,"h":900,"caption":"SIENA","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":18,"place_id":"piacenza-italy","lon":9.6665313,"lat":44.8476352,"place":"Piacenza, Italy","date":"2017-04-22","role":"transit_stop","quote":"At Piacenza we stopped to visit a church in the style of Bramante but it was closed.","images":[{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0288_L_1.webp","w":829,"h":403,"caption":"Siena Campanile","type":"photo"}]},{"seq":20,"place_id":"murs-et-gelignieux-france","lon":5.6630624,"lat":45.6400508,"place":"Murs-et-Gélignieux, France","date":"2017-04-22","role":"overnight_base","quote":"French bread. Bugs, Surfs, sunset, sunshine.","images":[]},{"seq":21,"place_id":"abbaye-notre-dame-des-dombes-le-plantay-france","lon":5.096353,"lat":46.0381956,"place":"Abbaye Notre-Dame des Dombes, Le Plantay, France","date":"2017-04-22","role":"main_stop","quote":"The monks were invited in 1860, to drain the lakes because the average age was only 20-30.","images":[]},{"seq":22,"place_id":"saint-jean-de-vaux-france","lon":4.6991922,"lat":46.8088442,"place":"Saint-Jean-de-Vaux, France","date":"2017-04-22","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We have waited 25 years to have supper in the St. Jean de Vaux restaurant, but it has always been closed in August.","images":[{"src":"media/2017-grand-tour-france-italy-reims-cinque/B_0289_R_1.webp","w":900,"h":827,"caption":"Cistercian Abbey Notre Dame des Dombes 01330 le Plantay","type":"photo"}]},{"seq":23,"place_id":"arras-france","lon":2.7772211,"lat":50.291048,"place":"Arras, France","date":"2017-04-22","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We had to move the van into the middle of the square because of the market the next day.","images":[]},{"seq":24,"place_id":"vimy-france","lon":2.8107935,"lat":50.3732652,"place":"Vimy, France","date":"2017-04-22","role":"main_stop","quote":"So many towns & villages have lost their bakeries.","images":[]},{"seq":25,"place_id":"coquelles-eurotunnel","lon":1.8147,"lat":50.9228,"place":"Coquelles (Eurotunnel)","date":"2017-04-22","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"Vimy ridge steep. Lots of Canadian [?&] memorials. On to the Tunnel.","images":[]}]}